OL,3,CMother's son, 9, developed eating
OL,4,Cdisorder after infected water crisis
OL,6,FWatch Sam Blackledge's report on how
OL,7,FJen's son was affected by
OL,8,Fcryptosporidiosis.
OL,10,FA mother from Brixham whose nine-year-
OL,11,Fold son has developed a serious eating
OL,12,Fdisorder following last year's
OL,13,Fcryptosporidium crisis is taking legal
OL,14,Faction against South West Water.
OL,16,FToday marks one year since the
OL,17,Fbacteria was confirmed to have entered
OL,18,Fthe town's water system, causing weeks
OL,19,Fof disruption and a public health
OL,20,Fcrisis.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G1/10
