OL,3,CMother's son, 9, developed eating
OL,4,Cdisorder after infected water crisis
OL,6,FHundreds of people became ill, and the
OL,7,Fnumber affected could turn out to be
OL,8,Fmuch higher than first thought.
OL,10,F'He hasn't had a meal since before 7
OL,11,FMay last year'
OL,13,FSpeaking to ITV News West Country, Jen
OL,14,FWatts says her son began showing signs
OL,15,Fof the illness before the outbreak was
OL,16,Fconfirmed.
OL,18,F"This time last year, on May 7th, my
OL,19,Flittle boy started to become unwell,"
OL,20,Fshe said.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G2/10
