OL,3,CMother's son, 9, developed eating
OL,4,Cdisorder after infected water crisis
OL,6,F"Come 13 May, he'd basically not eaten
OL,7,For drunk hardly anything.
OL,9,F"I was getting very concerned and I
OL,10,Fdidn't have an explanation. So I took
OL,11,Fhim to the hospital, and they sent us
OL,12,Fhome, and then that night the news
OL,13,Fbroke about the water situation with
OL,14,Fthe cryptosporidium.
OL,16,F"I took him back to A&E - he was very,
OL,17,Fvery poorly. He lost a huge amount of
OL,18,Fweight. He wasn't eating or drinking,
OL,19,Fhad diarrhoea; very bad reflux;
OL,20,Finability to swallow.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G3/10
