OL,3,CMother's son, 9, developed eating
OL,4,Cdisorder after infected water crisis
OL,6,F"As he himself says, it changed me,
OL,7,Fmummy," Jen said.
OL,9,F"It has been a horrendous year.
OL,10,FBecause he won't eat or drink or have
OL,11,Fhis meal replacement drinks outside of
OL,12,Fthe house, it's become very
OL,13,Frestrictive to what we can do and
OL,14,Fwhere we can go.
OL,16,F"He would never have developed Arfid
OL,17,Fif it wasn't for the Cryptosporidium.
OL,18,FEverything that's happened in this
OL,19,Flast year is a direct result of the
OL,20,FCryptosporidium and South West Water's
OL,21,Fnegligence.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G5/10
