OL,3,CMother's son, 9, developed eating
OL,4,Cdisorder after infected water crisis
OL,6,F"Their negligence caused the situation
OL,7,Fin the first place," she said. "Their
OL,8,Fresponse at the time and their
OL,9,Fimmediate denial of the situation was
OL,10,Fwoeful.
OL,12,F"To have allowed something like this
OL,13,Fto cause the problems it's caused for
OL,14,Fmy son, that are going to cause him
OL,15,Fproblems for the rest of his life, is
OL,16,Fjust, frankly, unforgivable."
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G7/10
