OL,6,F'Life-changing impacts'JJen is now one
OL,7,Fof several people taking legal action
OL,8,Fagainst South West Water. She hopes
OL,9,Ffor a settlement to pay for the help
OL,10,Fher son will need over the coming
OL,11,Fyears.
OL,13,FJatinder Paul, from Irwin Mitchell
OL,14,FSolicitors, says he is currently
OL,15,Frepresenting more than 20 people in
OL,16,FBrixham.
OL,18,F"A lot of our clients have had life-
OL,19,Fchanging impacts from this
OL,20,Fcryptosporidium outbreak," he said.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G8/10
