OL,4,Cdisorder after infected water crisis
OL,6,F"Some of them have gone on to
OL,7,Fexperience conditions such as
OL,8,Firritable bowel syndrome, some have
OL,9,Fhad psychological impacts.
OL,11,F"And in light of that, some of our
OL,12,Fclients now will require lifelong
OL,13,Ftreatment or therapies to be able to
OL,14,Fmove on from this."
OL,16,FIn a statement, South West Water said:
OL,17,F"We know the rare event in Brixham had
OL,18,Fa significant impact on local people
OL,19,Fand businesses and for that we are
OL,20,Ftruly sorry.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G9/10
