OL,6,F"While we cannot comment on live
OL,7,Fcases, in line with our customer
OL,8,Fpromise we have settled all claims as
OL,9,Fsoon as we have received the
OL,10,Finformation needed from claimants.
OL,12,F"We have settled over 97.5 per cent of
OL,13,Fall the claims that have been made
OL,14,Frelating to this incident and we are
OL,15,Fworking to settle any remaining claims
OL,16,Fas quickly as possible."
